<br>
1. Vamps are killed by wooden stakes, usually in the chest but the upperbody will work.<br>
<br>
2. The thing about the crucifix, it doesn't have to be silver, as long as it is blessed it works, again, silver is for werewolves, but a silver crucifix will work, but only if it is blessed.<br>
<br>
3. Garlic doesn't kill, it is kinda like Vamps kryptonite, it only weakens. <br>
<br>
4. If a vamp is exposed to enough sunlight it will die, if not, it will only loose like a limb or something like that.<br>
<br>
5. Ummm, oh, there are some holy chants that work, but they are in latin and a a pain in th butt to find and write.<br>
<br>
So, if you want any advice or help, just email me, or something at jonat7030@hotmail.com<br>
<br>
Oh yeah, Vamps blend in perfectly with humans, they control the length of their fangs, they lengthen when about to bit. Other than that they have no distinct makrings, except, oh what was it, I think it was two scars on their neck, even if they were born a vampire they have the scars, that is a marking. And only one vampire has the ability to turn into a bat, and that is the head honcho vamp, yep your guessed it, Dracula. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=neoangel>NeoAngel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(2/22/02 9:53:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=494.topic&index=30>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Really?</span><hr size=1> Nar, I did a bit of research. Vamps don't like silver, it burns and a mortal wound with a silver weapon will kill them as easily as a stake. Garlic : the smell hurts them and if it is taken into the body (extract injected, or just swallowed) if it's a little bit they get sick and if it's a lot they die.<br>
I have a coupla ideas for character colouring etc.<br>
Earth: would be black kinda skin, wears earthy colours like browns and greys.<br>
Wind: very pale white. Would wear blue and white.<br>
Water: normal white. Would wear blue and green<br>
Fire: White, red hair (a bit like burn's outta Psychic Force). Would wear reds oranges and yellows.<br>
